  Dependencies
  ============

Ubuntu:
- libdevel-cover-perl
- liblog-log4perl-perl
- libbsd-arc4random-perl
- libjson-xs-perl
- libio-socket-ssl-perl
- libdigest-sha-perl
- libstring-random-perl

OpenBSD:
- p5-BSD-arc4random
- p5-Devel-Cover
- p5-DBD-SQLite
- p5-HTML-Parser
- p5-IO-Socket-SSL
- p5-JSON-XS
- p5-Log-Log4perl
- p5-String-Random


  Running Tests
  =============

$ prove
or
$ prove t/device_add.t

For test coverage reports:
$ prove :: -c
$ cover
